{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_08_01",
  "title": "川咲さくら 1話 頑張ります、コーチ！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日の練習、凄く良かったよ\nこれなら大阪公演も成功間違いなしだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The practice today was great.\nWith this‚ the Osaka performance will surely be a success.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにそう言ってもらえるなら\n安心です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you say so‚ {user}-san‚\nI’m relieved!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7625168641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.3958501975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピース初の全国ツアーも、そろそろ折り返しだ\nだいぶ疲れが溜まってるだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re almost halfway through Sunny Peace’s first national tour.\nYou must be pretty tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "明日と明後日は久しぶりのオフだ。英気を養ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have a long-awaited break tomorrow and the day after. Recharge yourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4892730712,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.1808142502
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あのー、そのオフなんですけど\n付き合ってほしい所があるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ about the break…\nI have a place I’d like to go with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.8474809169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　別にいいけど、どうして俺なんだ？\nせっかくのオフだし、メンバー同士で行けば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? That’s fine‚ but why me?\nIt’s a precious day off‚ why don’t you go with the other members…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.0601334571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、{user}さんに\nお願いしたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ {user}-san‚\nI want to go with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3601334571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのためにも、力を貸してもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the fans‚ could you lend me a hand?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0268016497,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "近い、近いって。分かったから内容を話してくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re too close‚ too close! I get it‚ so just tell me what it’s about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6934667905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.6379562537
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "私、応援したい人がいるんです\nそのために、力を貸してほしくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to cheer for someone up.\nThat’s why I want your help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0046229203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "応援……？　もしかして、全国ツアーを回りながら\nファンの願いを叶える、あの企画か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cheer…? Is this about that project where you go around\nthe country on tour and fulfill fans’ wishes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.5007454235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "はい。大阪では私が\nソフトボール部の応援をすることになったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. In Osaka‚ I am\nsupposed to cheer for the softball team.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも、今までずっとメンバーが足りなくて\n試合が出来なかったみたいなんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said they haven’t been able to play any games\nbecause they didn’t have enough members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3007454235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.2340820629
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "ようやく九人目のメンバーが見つかったから\n初めての練習試合をするそうなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But they finally found their ninth member‚\nso they’re going to have their first practice game.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.327493792,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、応援のメッセージを下さいって\n私宛にお手紙が届いたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why someone sent me a letter\nasking for a message of support.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7007517814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.4007517814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（なるほど。つまりソフトボール部に贈る応援動画を）\n（俺に撮影してほしいってことか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I see. So she wants me to film a cheering video）\n（to be sent to the softball team.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。そういうことなら手伝うよ。明日はよろしく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. If that’s the case‚ I’ll help you. See you tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.576868232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.4777752558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　助かります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much! I’m so relieved!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4777752558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.7777752558
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "動画の撮影には最近慣れてきたんだ\n編集も多少は出来ると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve gotten used to filming videos recently.\nI think I can do some editing too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.1991786478
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "動画？　編集？　なんの話ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Videos? Editing? What are you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1991786478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2991786478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4334311303,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.6603088000074,
          "startTime": 117.8000914391
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.4667654809
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.4667654809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "見て下さい、{user}さん\n立派なグラウンドですね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ {user}-san.\nIt’s a splendid field~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.6000914391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "まさか現地で直接応援するつもりとは……俺が甘かった\nでも練習試合は明日なんだろ？　どうして今日学校に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought you’d come here to cheer for them in person… I was too naive.\nBut the practice game is tomorrow‚ right? Why are you at the school today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8333455403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.2672784147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "ソフトボール部のみんなに会うためです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To meet everyone on the softball team.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.2672784147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_08_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "応援する相手のことをよく知っていた方が\n気持ちを一杯込められると思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I could put more feeling into it\nif I understand the people I’m cheering for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.3339466073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
